Vindicator is a full featured user management plugin for Bukkit based
Minecraft servers.

Features:
  - CraftIRC integration
  - Local storage
    - MySQL
    - SQLite
  - Integration with global banning systems
    - MCBans
    - MCBouncer
  - IP logging
    - Alerts for alternate accounts
  - IP/Player banning
    - Support for IPv4
    - Support for IPV6
    - Ban types
      - Permanent
      - Temporary
  - IP/Player kicking
  - IP/Player noting
    - Importance levels
      - Severe
      - Warning
      - Information
    - Visibility levels
      - Public
      - Private
  - Player tickets
